headline: Zimmer Biomet price target raised to $118 from $117 at Truist
summary: Truist raised the firm’s price target on Zimmer Biomet (ZBH) to $118 from $117 and keeps a Hold rating on the shares as part of a broader research note previewing 2025 in Medical Technology.
